Founded in 1987
The world's first dedicated semiconductor foundry, with fabs in Taiwan, U.S.A. and China 
2019 total capacity exceeded 12 million 12-inch equivalent wafers
2019 total revenue reached a new high at US$34.6 billion
Owns a total of 39,118 patents as of December 31, 2019 
Selected as a component of Dow Jones Sustainability Indices (DJSI) for 19 consecutive years in 2019; Elected  Semiconductors and Semiconductor Equipment Industry Group Leader for three consecutive years (2013~2015)

